    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ann1_t",
      "x": 12,
      "y": 147,
      "width": 370,
      "height": 167,
      "text": "Performance Annotations:\n\n* Streaming is incremental - each yield re-renders only the\n  changed subtree, not the full terminal\n\n* Backpressure: Ink batches renders via react-reconciler -\n  no render storm on rapid yields (16ms batch window)\n\n* Typeahead: Prompt input stays responsive during streaming -\n  it's a separate React subtree",
      "originalText": "Performance Annotations:\n\n* Streaming is incremental - each yield re-renders only the\n  changed subtree, not the full terminal\n\n* Backpressure: Ink batches renders via react-reconciler -\n  no render storm on rapid yields (16ms batch window)\n\n* Typeahead: Prompt input stays responsive during streaming -\n  it's a separate React subtree",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#718096",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5003,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 5004,
      "isDeleted": false,
