    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "insight_t",
      "x": 408,
      "y": 149,
      "width": 365,
      "height": 167,
      "text": "Key Insight:\n\nInk gives us React's declarative model in the terminal -\nthe streaming pipeline is identical whether rendering to\nDOM or TTY, just the reconciler target changes.\n\nReactDOM reconciler  ->  DOM nodes\nInk reconciler       ->  VT100 escape sequences\n\nSame React mental model. Different rendering target.",
      "originalText": "Key Insight:\n\nInk gives us React's declarative model in the terminal -\nthe streaming pipeline is identical whether rendering to\nDOM or TTY, just the reconciler target changes.\n\nReactDOM reconciler  ->  DOM nodes\nInk reconciler       ->  VT100 escape sequences\n\nSame React mental model. Different rendering target.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#6C63FF",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
